Use Case: Run Provider Reports
Context: A report is sent to all providers of ChocAn either automatically on Friday at midnight or manually by the ChocAn Manager.
Actors: ChocAn Manager
Main Success Scenario:
	1.System detects that it is midnight on Friday.
	2.System generates reports for all providers that provided  to ChocAn.
	3.System sends the reports to providers involved via email attachment.
Extensions:
	1a. Manager chooses a provider to send a report to.
	1b. System generates a report for that provider.
	1c. Use case resumes at step 3.